Neobanker前后端接口规范文档

概述

本文档旨在定义前后端交互的接口规范，以确保开发过程中前后端能够高效、准确地进行数据交换。接口规范包括请求方法、请求参数、响应体结构、错误处理等方面的规定。

AccountController

login

**

请求URL

/account/login POST

返回结果

{
	"email":"string",
	"userName":"string",
	"phoneNumber":"string",
	"passWord":"string",
	"role":"string",
	"status":"string"
}

register

**

请求URL

/account/register POST

返回结果

{
	"email":"string",
	"userName":"string",
	"phoneNumber":"string",
	"passWord":"string",
	"role":"string",
	"status":"string"
}

getAccount

**

请求URL

/account/{email}/get GET

返回结果

{
	"email":"string",
	"userName":"string",
	"phoneNumber":"string",
	"passWord":"string",
	"role":"string",
	"status":"string"
}

deleteAccount

**

请求URL

/account/{email}/delete DELETE

返回结果

Void{}

resetPassword

**

请求URL

/account/{email}/reset-password PUT

返回结果

Void{}

importComapanySearch

**

请求URL

/account/import POST

返回结果

string{}
